{"tid":1945540,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"生化危機 3 重製版中「918」讓中國玩家感冒犯","createTime":"2020-03-27T06:34:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-28T14:24:45.000Z","uid":41380,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"9c660b4d843d6ba10ed07d63e320400a59c58cfd","tid":1945540,"uid":41380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T06:34:32.000Z","msg":"近日 Capcom 推出了《生化危機 3 重製版》的試玩版，以讓大家體驗重製版與舊作的分別。不過，有中國玩家遊玩過後指，遊戲內的密碼數字有冒犯中國之嫌。<br />\n《生化危機 3 重製版》試玩版的遊玩時間只有 5 分鐘左右，當中有個關卡需要在保險箱上輸入密碼，而密碼提示印在一張海報上，玩家推測後可得出三位密碼「918」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2KHDGkz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2KHDGkz.jpg&h=8a7c3f52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有中國玩家就指此數字讓其聯想到被日軍侵占的九一八事變，直感冒犯。更有中國玩家表示，如正式版未有對此作出修正，便會作出給《還願》和《我的英雄學院》一樣的差評。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/igTb1kS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FigTb1kS.png&h=cc435c79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iJnHozc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiJnHozc.png&h=3b97cd70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x12L5Ny.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx12L5Ny.png&h=242f1dfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qd33Ssy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqd33Ssy.png&h=6b24df34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hEAxLNy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhEAxLNy.jpg&h=8476fa56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不過，不少中國玩家與台灣玩家都認為這件事情過於牽強，並質疑是否與中國歷史有關的數字，如「64」、「128」等都通通不能使用，指某部份中國玩家過於「玻璃心」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UGOSLNH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUGOSLNH.png&h=8070fb82&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bd928a8b157763d1d885f703997b4cec03c04222","tid":1945540,"uid":41380,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T06:35:04.000Z"